---
<section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
            
            <div class="w-32 h-32 md:w-48 md:h-48 flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border-4 border-slate-800 shadow-lg relative z-10">
                <img src="/khairul.jpg" alt="Khairul Azri" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 text-display">Built by a Marketer, Not Just a Coder.</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    "Hi, I'm <strong class="text-white">Khairul Azri</strong>. By day, I am an <strong class="text-blue-400">Integrated Marketing Manager</strong> leading tech-driven growth strategies. By night, I build high-performance websites for business owners who care about ROI, not just pretty pixels."
                </p>
                
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/khairulazri/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0077b5] hover:bg-[#006396] text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors font-medium text-sm shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/30">
                    <i data-lucide="linkedin" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                    View Professional Profile
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>